{"type": "article", "id": 2378, "title": "用黑胶唱片做的梳子", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-16T15:15:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222237PUHnhGDdiXomlpvF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>黑胶唱片如今已变成一种带有怀旧感的物品。近日，Upstairs 商店将黑胶唱片制作成了梳子，这款极具复古风格的梳子有两个款式，一款是 No.15 ，有着厚厚的梳齿，并增加了梳齿的缝隙，男士们可以用它来梳理不整齐的卷曲胡子，另一款则是 No.20 ,有着宽且薄的梳齿，适用于女士们梳理长发。每把梳子上都保留着原先黑胶唱片的环线，以纪念它曾经的功能。定价 9 欧元</span>，<a href=\"http://www.upstairs-shop.com/categories/clothes-accessories/grably-comb.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222234lEu2YIWs0NbDBrfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222235VhC5IvANfsqtlna6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222236hnlFP3IBrEmKCqS5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222236QMP0TzWyBVmXaCqx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}